#: ../../source/developer_guide/extending_http_api.rst:2
msgid "Extending the HTTP API"
msgstr "扩展 HTTP API"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/extending_http_api.rst:4
msgid ""
"You can add new endpoints to the ``lmcache server`` HTTP frontend "
"**without modifying any existing code**. An endpoint is just a Python "
"module placed in ``lmcache/v1/multiprocess/http_apis/`` that exposes a "
"FastAPI ``APIRouter``; ``HTTPAPIRegistry`` auto-discovers and mounts it "
"at startup -- the same zero-modification pattern used by the :doc:`L2 "
"adapters </mp/l2_storage/index>`."
msgstr "您可以向 ``lmcache server`` HTTP 前端添加新的端点 **而无需修改任何现有代码**。端点只是放置在 ``lmcache/v1/multiprocess/http_apis/`` 中的 Python 模块，它暴露了一个 FastAPI ``APIRouter``；``HTTPAPIRegistry`` 在启动时自动发现并挂载它——与 :doc:`L2 adapters </mp/l2_storage/index>` 使用的零修改模式相同。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/extending_http_api.rst:12
msgid "How discovery works"
msgstr "发现是如何工作的"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/extending_http_api.rst:14
msgid ""
"At startup, ``http_server.py`` hands the FastAPI app to "
"``HTTPAPIRegistry`` (``lmcache/v1/multiprocess/http_api_registry.py``), "
"which scans the ``http_apis/`` directory with ``pkgutil``, imports every "
"module whose name ends with ``_api``, and includes any module-level "
"``router``. The built-in modules follow this pattern:"
msgstr "在启动时，``http_server.py`` 将 FastAPI 应用程序交给 ``HTTPAPIRegistry``（``lmcache/v1/multiprocess/http_api_registry.py``），该注册器使用 ``pkgutil`` 扫描 ``http_apis/`` 目录，导入所有名称以 ``_api`` 结尾的模块，并包含任何模块级的 ``router``。内置模块遵循此模式："

